headline: Delta Recognized as One of Taiwan's Top 5 Best Global Brands, Achieving Record High Brand Value with Superior 30% YoY Growth
summary: Delta, a global leader in power management and a provider of smart green solutions, has ascended to the Top 5 within the "2025 Best Taiwan Global Brands", its highest ranking after 15 consecutive years of recognition. According to the survey by Interbrand, Delta's brand value surged by 30% YoY to US$773 million, a new record for the company.
